and exchange rate effects.
Net debt rose slightly to Pounds 1.77m at the year end, against Pounds
1.54m, for gearing of 25 per cent (23 per cent). The company said that an
inventory reduction programme had released Pounds 724,000 towards the cost
of capital investment.
