<TEXT>
The main foreign shareholders in the United Bank for Africa (UBA), one of
Nigeria's three biggest commercial banks, have said they aim to pull out of
the bank, Reuter reports from Lagos.
Mr Luke Okafor, UBA's managing director, said Banque Nationale de Paris
