Over nine years
 -----------------------------------------------------------------------
Pounds 52,800
 -----------------------------------------------------------------------
CUSTOMER C has been attracted by the low cost-per-copy on longer
contracts. He has taken out a nine-year contract with 15% per annum
service price escalation. He also has lease charges 25% higher than the
base case. After three-years he has paid pounds 11,800 and is committed
to pay another pounds 41,000 over the remaining six years.
